

1.Download thrift from http://thrift.apache.org/download/ and extract
2.sudo apt-get install libboost-dev libboost-test-dev libboost-program-options-dev libevent-dev automake libtool flex bison pkg-config g++ libssl-dev 
3.install ruby and rails
4.gem install rspec
5.gem install mongrel
6.from the thrift directory do ./configure
7.make
8.sudo make install 

Possible errors

rake aborted 
all the following gems should be installed. The error msg will display the name of the missing gem.
ruby-dev librspec-ruby rake rubygems libdaemons-ruby libgemplugin-ruby mongrel

Also downlaod the python-dev for python related errors.
